{"tid":1439770,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人既Online-香城Online","createTime":"2019-08-10T08:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T09:29:17.000Z","uid":226671,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec67614af76eb7c791ee346c5480264217d759e","tid":1439770,"uid":226671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yGDN1sb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyGDN1sb.png&h=c76e6886&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n在過去兩個月,大家都好沉默迷這遊戲，呢個遊戲出現左很多角色，但大家要記住我地都係香港人，我地吃同一個催淚彈，見到速龍一齊跑。所謂勇武，和理非都係一班愛香港的人變成的。希望各位可以做到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>不割蓆 不內訌 不分化</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"0eee67f03004f77b2c11c3ab5711e4d6b2b23b14","tid":1439770,"uid":142872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f785455c7487bdf0776cb456616fb17d5e6798a","tid":1439770,"uid":36961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}